longBusinessSummary: Duo World, Inc., an information technology and software solutions company, develops customer life cycle management, customer care, and contact center management solutions in Sri Lanka and internationally. The company's products include DuoSubscribe, a cloud-based solution for subscription management and billing; FaceTone, a communication and collaboration platform that offers call conferencing, call parking, call forwarding, voicemail, call routing, and chat-based collaboration solutions; and SmoothFlow, a tool that allows businesses to develop and deploy conversational automation. It also provides a business intelligence and data visualization tool. The company serves banks, retail chains, Pay-TV operators, and financial conglomerates. Duo World, Inc. was founded in 2004 and is based in Henderson, Nevada.
